{"word":"H6793 - צִנָּה - tsinnâh - tsin-naw' - Buckler","slug":"H6793","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">צִנָּה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>tsinnâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tsin-naw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Buckler"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E6;&#x05E0;&#x05BC;&#x05D4; - tsinna&#x0302;h</b> - <i>tsin-naw'</i><p/>Feminine of <a href=\"#/H6791\">H6791</a>; a <i>hook</i> (as <i>pointed</i>); also a (large) <i>shield</i> (as if guarding by <i>prickliness</i>); also <i>cold</i> (as <i>piercing</i>): - buckler, cold, hook, shield, target."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6803\">H6803</a>"}]}